      <title>华尔街看多里拉，对土耳其政策逆转持乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/wall-street-goes-long-lira-in-optimism-on-turkey-policy-reversal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于离岸和在岸收益率之间的差距扩大，花旗集团和摩根大通等银行建议买入土耳其里拉，这表明外国投资者正在通过衍生品押注土耳其里拉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/wall-street-goes-long-lira-in-optimism-on-turkey-policy-reversal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 11:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
